&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an &lt;strong&gt;Intelligence Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; at Rhombus, you will create impactful intelligence assessments on topics including foreign military activities, weapons development, global conflicts, and international stability to support India and Allied national security decision making. Analysts will fuse Rhombus’s unique AI-derived data with a spectrum of open-source information to create these products.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;strong&gt;Intelligence Analysts&lt;/strong&gt; routinely perform thorough research and analysis across global security issues guided by client intelligence needs. Outputs are primarily delivered through written intelligence assessments that align with Indian Intelligence Community standards, as well as tailored briefings for internal and external audiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates must excel in high-pressure collaborative work and demonstrate strong interpersonal skills; Team success relies on close coordination within the intelligence team and with cross-functional partners. We&#39;re seeking those that are comfortable giving and receiving feedback to enhance collective output and quality.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful candidates will be &lt;em&gt;solution-oriented self-starters&lt;/em&gt; who are tech-savvy, able to identify problems and opportunities, and capable of proposing solutions in a dynamic, fast-paced environment. The ability to multitask and prioritize is essential given the pace of global events and evolving client needs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a candidate with deep subject matter expertise in defense, military capabilities, weapons systems, and emerging security developments. The ideal candidate will be able to apply their regional and functional expertise to produce a high volume of high-quality analytic assessments under tight deadlines and with minimal review. This is a &#39;roll up your sleeves&#39; role with ample opportunity for growth.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
